																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "h0ff194c6g6c48g44e5g8c54gd84425a54d40",
																	"value": "Karlach. I am glad you can enjoy the touch of another once again... and I hope you are afforded much more time than you have been told. A lifetime and more, if I have a say in it.",
																	"type": 28,
																	"version": 2
