																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "hc221ebb4g110ag416ag8216g8299da39165b",
																	"value": "My heart grows heavy for Karlach. She can touch, once more... yet is her remaining time to truly be so short? I shall pray to Silvanus that it does not come to pass.",
